# venue
 
 - 2 work areas which are each 12 feet wide
 - independent internet connection to NYC mesh
 - big screen visible from outside venue
 - operators/stewards
 - content creators
 - teachers of trash magic, trash robot, geometron
 - makers/builders
 - universally accessible 
 - transit accessible
 - available toilet and fresh water
 - available free power
 - free and open to all as for as much time as possible
 - trash magic media feed points back to venue, brings in media content creators(trash magicians)
 - full field kit for trash robot camp: solar power, battery, USB charger, bags of media